OL,3,CBirmingham Airport passengers
OL,4,Cevacuated after report of smoke in
OL,5,Cbaggage reclaim
OL,7,FPassengers have been evacuated from
OL,8,Fthe North Terminal of Birmingham
OL,9,FAirport after an incident.
OL,11,FFire crews were called to the scene at
OL,12,Freports of smoke in the baggage
OL,13,Freclaim and immigration area on
OL,14,FTuesday, April 7th.
OL,16,FPassengers were evacuated from this
OL,17,Farea as a precaution.
