OL,3,CBirmingham Airport passengers
OL,4,Cevacuated after report of smoke in
OL,5,Cbaggage reclaim
OL,7,FA West Midlands Fire Service
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "Firefighters are
OL,9,Fat the airport, after reports of smoke
OL,10,Fin a baggage reclaim area.
OL,12,F"There is no confirmed fire, and we
OL,13,Fare working with on-site staff to
OL,14,Fidentify the source of the smoke."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
