OL,3,CBirmingham Airport passengers
OL,4,Cevacuated after report of smoke in
OL,5,Cbaggage reclaim
OL,7,FA Birmingham Airport spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "Following the evacuation of
OL,9,Fbaggage reclaim and immigration areas
OL,10,Fin the North Terminal, West Midlands
OL,11,FFire Service has confirmed it is safe
OL,12,Ffor passengers to return, as the
OL,13,Fincident is now resolved.
OL,15,F"We are working to move all displaced
OL,16,Fpassengers back into the terminal as
OL,17,Fquickly as possible. We apologise for
OL,18,Fthe inconvenience this has caused some
OL,19,Fof our passengers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
